title: Bug 116609[Regression]Color orange doesn't work.
description: Bug 116609[Regression]Color orange doesn't work. Description:Color orange doesn't work.Steps to reproduce:1.
OB: When setting the color or background color of a report item to orange, the color does not display as expected.
EB: The color or background color of a report item set to orange should display correctly.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Insert a report item. 
2. Set the color or background color of the report item to orange. 
3. Observe that the color does not appear as expected.
